reviewText: Such a great series. Wish all the seasons were in Region One. Why not??
As in the first 6 series, Amanda is brilliant as Dr. Sam Ryan.  She is on the ball even when no one else is in the game... Just great mysteries...
Another top quality drama starring top quality actors who give a stirring pereformance1 I'm hooked on this stuff! Best to get the whole set and watch all the sequences unfold!
